Welcome to Voight-Kampff test's documentation!¶

Voight-Kampff test is a test used by the LAPD's Blade Runners to assist in determining whether or not an individual was a replicant.

Note

It typically took twenty to thirty cross-referenced questions to detect a Nexus-6 replicant.
